Series V. (RESTRICTED) Duplicate print matter and ephemera

Boxes in this series only contain excess copies of print matter and ephemera found elsewhere in this record group. Because the material is redundant it is not available for regular Reading Read use but is reserved for exhibition or other special uses only for exhibition purposes.
